In less than no time, @cosrx ‘s advance snail 96 mucin power essence has become my holy grail. And now I can’t live without it. It definitely made my skin more glowy and hydrated🔆✨💗
I use this day and night and noticed skin texture and hyperpigmentation, including post acne marks, lightened after a week of using it. And when my skin gets irritated or flares up, this instantly calms it down.

✨Benefits and Features✨

🔆 Hydrates and Soothes: Provides intense hydration and soothes sensitive skin.
🔆 Improves Skin Elasticity: Helps to improve skin elasticity and reduce the appearance of fine lines and wrinkles.
🔆Repairs and Regenerates: Repairs and regenerates damaged skin cells.
🔆Cruelty-Free and Vegan-Friendly: Free from animal testing and vegan-friendly.
🔆Non-Comedogenic: Does not clog pores.
